IDEA Inc said it signed aletter of intent to buy privately-held StructuralInstrumentation Inc.    The purchase, for an undisclosed sum, will be made mostlywith IDEA common stock, the company said.    IDEA said the purchase will add about 32 cts per share toits fiscal 1988 earnings.    IDEA reported earnings of four cts per share for thequarter ended October 31, 1986. Reuter&#3;